Title: Playboy Gift Set - Malibu(Set of 2)
Description: Playboy fragrances rule the roost of the men’s premium fragrances with their blazing and icy perfumes which capture the essence of the contemporary urbane man. With impressive sillage, the fragrances from the house of Playboy usually lend a smoky edge to your personality making it the perfect gift for the quintessential bachelor. This Playboy Gift Set is one which captures the wildness of Malibu in its enticing blue depths. The set of two includes an Eau de Toilette which is perfect for date night and a deodorant spray that carries forward the good vibes to the morning after. As the flight descends, the shimmering lights of the swanky town of Malibu beckon you; white, sandy beaches brighten your days up while your mansion party throbs with the power of the music at night. You become the Malibu man, caught up in your own personal paradise, enslaving your senses in the flowing champagne and the seductiveness of Playboy Malibu Eau de Toilette. Unbuttoned linen shirt billowing in the wind, aviators reflecting the beautiful women who glance appreciatively and the mass premium coloring you with its unique charm - this is why you are irresistible. Dab on the Eau de Toilette as you head out to the hottest club in town and make sure you’re never at a loss for delightful company. Take off on a long drive with the wheels of the car kicking up the surf into foamy sprays of exhilaration as the energy of the composition overtakes you. Perfumer John Gamba experiments with flavors in Playboy Malibu with vivacious opening notes of crunchy apple, light mint, zesty verbena and neroli. The heart is a mystery of cold iris, woody cedar, spicy coriander and soothing jasmine that rests on a base of warm musk, sandalwood, tonka bean and the beautiful redolence of cashmere. Malibu is presented in a dark flacon with the Playboy bunny peeking playfully on one side. The azure depths of the fragrance itself reflect the chromatic tones of the vast ocean. Launched in 2008, Playboy Malibu is a fragrance exclusively for the man who lets the pulse of the city guide him through it all. The Playboy Malibu Deodorant Spray is the fragrance that lets you carry over the memories of the parties that blew your mind into the next day when you can flounder in the smoothness of the lasting notes and reminiscence about good times even when work surrounds you. Present the man in your life with this versatile gift set and watch Playboy Malibu work its magic on him.

You stepped into your bedroom and saw yourself in the mirror, it was the end of the day but you still looked so beautiful because of this unique Coloressence Blusher.
